    "text": "with the words you learned here."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.24,
    "end": 6,
    "text": "Today we travel to the past, a long time in the past."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.24,
    "end": 3.68,
    "text": "Some dinosaurs ate only plants."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.24,
    "end": 3.44,
    "text": "In the time of dinosaurs."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.32,
    "end": 7.12,
    "text": "Many millions of years ago, these animals lived on Earth, but now they do not."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.32,
    "end": 2.96,
    "text": "Daisy, remember, be polite."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.32,
    "end": 4.32,
    "text": "You can say, Max, would you please tell me the question?"
