    "text": "I would love to see real dinosaurs."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.32,
    "end": 4.8,
    "text": "Now there are no more dinosaurs."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.32,
    "end": 2.7199999999999998,
    "text": "So let's go back to Anna."
