  {
    "start": 0.64,
    "end": 3.44,
    "text": "Max, would you please tell me the question?"
  },
  {
    "start": 0.72,
    "end": 7.12,
    "text": "Well, many scientists say a large rock in space hit the Earth."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.96,
    "end": 4.72,
    "text": "The question is, where are the dinosaurs?"
  },
  {
    "start": 0.96,
    "end": 6.96,
    "text": "Max, I am ready to see some real dinosaurs."
  },
  {
    "start": 0.96,
    "end": 4.4,
    "text": "We call them fossils."
  },
  {
    "start": 1.28,
    "end": 6.8,
    "text": "A long time ago, there were many dinosaurs on Earth."
  },
  {
    "start": 1.6800000000000002,
    "end": 4.32,
    "text": "I would love to see dinosaurs."
  },
  {
    "start": 2.4,
    "end": 9.12,
